•	Formulate Migration technical design to migrate an EBS Installed Base centric solution to a Concept Wave Service Registry. Designed and Implemented ETL framework to source data from multiple systems and transform into the multiple target system in line with the complex Migration strategy.

Lead COTS products (TimeKeeper and VMS) project which are based on Card based solutions with responsibilities;
•	Project lead for Standard and Customization of the product
•	Requirement analyst
